Gaoyang Lake Water Park was once the only place to pass the Kansai Bridge connecting Hanyang and Yicheng. Its Gaoyang Lake Water Park has an area of 300,000 pings and is the largest artificial lake water park in Asia. More than 90,000 pings of freshwater lakes have clear and clean water quality. The main facilities here include a full-length bicycle lane built along the waterside square, artificial island, etc., as well as a parking lot with 1050 cars, 3 children's playgrounds, nature learning fields, red-crowned crane feeding fields, music fountains, More than 100 wild flowers and more than 200,000 trees composed of leisure space, is a good place to learn nature, feel life, and here will also hold a variety of exhibitions such as the Gaoyang Flower Expo.

The lake water park is about an hour's drive from Seoul. The environment is quiet and quiet. It is one of the good places to go out in Seoul. There are also many famous gourmet restaurants nearby, such as the grilled fish restaurant fisherman grilled fish, and there is a flower expo in late September. The park covers a very large area and takes half a day to walk. In autumn, the past is all red, yellow and green, pleasing to the eye.
